<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/305000158/2025-26/syllabus/0> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 0 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "1. Oral communication"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/305000158/2025-26/syllabus/1> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 1 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "1.1. Importance and necessity of oral communication in a professional environment. Intellectual and emotional aspects of public speaking. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/305000158/2025-26/syllabus/10> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 10 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "2.4. Revision and editing of a text. Objectivity and criticism of a manuscript. Manuscript curating. Specific proofreading. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/305000158/2025-26/syllabus/11> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 11 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "2.5. Writing a research paper. The research process. Parts of a research paper: introduction, methods, results, conclusions. Citations. Criticism of a research paper. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/305000158/2025-26/syllabus/12> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 12 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "2.6. Writing for outreach. Understanding the audience. Simplification of the material. Visual resources. Media: web pages, videos, podcasts, journals. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/305000158/2025-26/syllabus/13> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 13 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "3. Outreach"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/305000158/2025-26/syllabus/14> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 14 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "3.1. Messages and contents. Selection of contents and messages. Communication channels and key steps. Capturing public interest. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/305000158/2025-26/syllabus/15> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 15 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "3.2. Outreach and popularization of mathematics. Use of an appropriate language. Distinction between the known and the unknown. Communicating the invisible. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/305000158/2025-26/syllabus/16> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 16 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "3.3. Science communication to the public. Visual communication. Verbal communication. Communicating through the mass media. Media framework. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/305000158/2025-26/syllabus/17> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 17 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "3.4. Organization of outreach activities: mathematics festivals, mathematics in the streets, conferences, theatrical performances; podcasts and video channels. Writing popular about mathematics. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/305000158/2025-26/syllabus/2> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 2 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "1.2. Basic principles of communication. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/305000158/2025-26/syllabus/3> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 3 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "1.3. Non-verbal language: body language, personal appearance, use of space, intonation. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/305000158/2025-26/syllabus/4> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 4 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "1.4. Content of speech. Originality and timeliness. Study of a topic. Organization of speech. Parts of speech. Types of speech. Speech writing. Speech assessment. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/305000158/2025-26/syllabus/5> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 5 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "1.5. Delivery of speech. Presentation style. The three features of classic speech: credibility, intellectual content, emotional content. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/305000158/2025-26/syllabus/6> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 6 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "2. Written communication"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/305000158/2025-26/syllabus/7> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 7 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "2.1. Writing as a means of communication. Writing as professional obligation for mathematicians. Intellectual, emotional, and moral aspects in writing. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/305000158/2025-26/syllabus/8> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 8 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "2.2. Creativity and writing. Generation of ideas: selection, order, and presentation. Sin subniveles"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/305000158/2025-26/syllabus/9> a ns1:SyllabusItem ;
    ns1:itemIndex 9 ;
    ns1:syllabusDescription "2.3. Initial drafts. Audience selection. Tone, rhythm, and register. Writing in spirals. Sin subniveles"@es .

